{"type":"assistant","uuid":"60dbc9c5-9399-46ee-b4c8-b98fdd04996f","session_id":"6fb4a7ca-0ecf-405e-b8d1-716d14984a49","parent_tool_use_id":null,"message":{"id":"60dbc9c5-9399-46ee-b4c8-b98fdd04996f","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qwen3.5-plus","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经了解了仓库的基本结构。这是一个 Python 异步机器人框架 NoneBot2。让我继续查看更多的配置信息，包括测试配置和目录结构。\n\n让我查看：\n1. tests 目录结构\n2. CONTRIBUTING.md 了解贡献指南和开发流程\n3. 是否有 Makefile\n4. nonebot 源码目录结构","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0}}}
